data.value: A: The game is compatible with Windows. To play the game smoothly, we recommend the following system requirements: Processor: Dual-core processor (Intel or AMD) Memory (RAM): 4GB or more Graphics: DirectX 11-compatible graphics card Storage: 10GB of available space Sound: DirectX-compatible sound card Internet: An internet connection is required for updates and online features.
